WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Semua orang wajib melindungi karya asli]

01:06.540 --> 01:10.820
[Wangi Abadi]

01:10.820 --> 01:11.980
[Diadaptasi dari novel "Qianxiangyin" karya Shisilang]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 16]

01:39.870 --> 01:40.460
Adik Seperguruan Lei.

01:43.350 --> 01:44.020
Adik Seperguruan Lei.

01:52.230 --> 01:53.540
Adik Kecil, kau sudah bekerja keras.

01:54.510 --> 01:56.410
Hanya kau yang masuk ke delapan besar dari Puncak Zhuiyu.

01:56.840 --> 01:57.490
Itu harus berterima kasih

01:57.510 --> 01:59.460
